Mutane 832 Sun Mutu a Tsunami da Ya Yi Tashin Tashin Tashin Aikin Kasa a Indonesia
Rahoton da Ofishin Kula da Bala'i ya fitar a safiyar ranar Lahadi ya ce, adadin mutanen da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka kashe a Indonesia ya kai 832.
Kakakin hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho ya shaidawa manema labarai cewa an samu rahoton cewa mutane da dama sun makale a cikin baraguron gine-gine bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 da aka ji a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayin mita 6.
Birnin Palu, mai mutane fiye da 380,000, yana cike da rushewar gine-gine.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekaru 32 bisa zargin kisan kai bayan da aka kashe wata mata da aka yi wa bulala.
An kaddamar da binciken kisan bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead, Merseyside, da safiyar yau.
An samu wata mata mai shekara 44 da aka yi wa bulala a karfe 7:55 na safe a Grayson Mews a kan titin John, kuma an kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 da ake zargi da kisan kai.
