Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron karar da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli labaran da 'yan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da Christine Blasey Ford suka bayar a tashoshin talabijin shida a ranar Alhamis, wata mata da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin da aka yi masa a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, an ci gaba da yin siyasa, kuma 'yan jarida sun katse shirin su na yau da kullum domin sanar da wani juyi a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da aka cimma da Jeff Flake, Sanata daga Arizona, cewa FBI za ta gudanar da binciken da aka yi na zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya sha giya ya yi mata fyade kuma ya yi kokarin cire mata tufafinta a wajen bikin makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya bayyana a cikin shaidar cewa ya tabbata cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne suka saurari sauraron da aka yi a ranar Jumma'a, kamar yadda rahoton kamfanin Nielsen ya nuna.
Kamfanin ya yi lissafin matsakaicin masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu adadin masu kallo ba a nan take ga sauran hanyoyin sadarwar da suka watsa sauraron, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma tana da matsala wajen auna yawan mutanen da suke kallon abubuwan da ke cikin ofisoshinta.
Don a ba ku karin haske, wannan taron yana da yawa kamar yadda ake kallon wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko kuma kyautar Oscar.
Tashar Fox News Channel wadda masu sauraron ta suka nuna goyon bayanta ga zaben Kavanaugh, ta samu mafi yawan masu sauraro da suka kai miliyan 5.69 a lokacin zaman zaman, in ji kamfanin Nielsen.
ABC ta zo ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
Kamfanin Nielsen ya ce CBS tana da masu kallo miliyan 3.1 NBC miliyan 2.94 MSNBC miliyan 2.89 CNN miliyan 2.52.
An ci gaba da samun sha'awa bayan an yi wa'azin.
Flake ne ya yi fice a wasan kwaikwayo da aka yi ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin wannan dan jam'iyyar mai tsaka-tsakin ya fitar da sanarwa cewa zai kada kuri'a a kan Kavanaugh, kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama shi da ke kururuwa a gaban masu zanga-zanga a safiyar Juma'a yayin da yake kokarin hawa kan lif don zuwa sauraron kwamitin shari'a.
Ya tsaya yana kallon mutane na minti da dama yayin da masu zanga-zanga suka yi masa ba'a a gaban kyamarorin CNN.
"Ina tsaye a gabanku", in ji wata mata.
Kuna ganin yana faɗin gaskiya ga ƙasar nan?
Suka ce masa, "Kai ne kake da iko, amma mata da yawa ba su da taimako".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da sanarwa kafin kofar lif ta rufe cewa zai yi karin bayani a taron kwamitin.
Bayan 'yan sa'o'i, duk tashoshin talabijin da na kebul sun biyo baya a lokacin da aka shirya cewa kwamitin shari'a zai yi zabe kan batun mika takarar Kavanaugh ga majalisar dattawa baki daya.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan har FBI ta binciki zargin da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda 'yan Democrat da ke cikin 'yan tsiraru suka bukaci.
Flake ya yi magana da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons, dan Democrat.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons, da kuma wasu 'yan majalisar dattawa, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Wannan hukunci na Flake yana da muhimmanci domin ya bayyana cewa 'yan Republican ba za su iya amincewa da Kavanaugh ba tare da bincike ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude wani bincike na FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
