An yi ta gwagwarmayar 'yan sanda da 'yan tawayen Catalonia a ranar tunawa da kada kuri'ar neman 'yancin kai
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan da masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai suka yi karo da 'yan sanda da suka shiga tsakani, kuma bayan da dubban mutane suka shiga zanga-zangar nuna rashin amincewa da zaben raba kan Catalonia.
Wasu 'yan tawaye da suka zo da tufafi da 'yan sanda suka ce su gafarce su, suka fara harba wa 'yan sanda ƙwai da kuma fenti, suna saukowa cikin duhu a kan titunan da za su cika da masu yawon buɗe ido.
An ci gaba da yin faɗa a baya bayan wannan rana, sa'ad da 'yan sanda suka yi amfani da sanduna don su kwantar da rikici.
A cikin sa'o'i da dama, ƙungiyoyin masu neman 'yancin kai sun yi ihu "Babu mantuwa, babu gafara", kuma a madadin su, 'yan ƙungiyar sun yi ihu "Rayuwar Spain".
An kwantar da mutane 14 a asibiti sakamakon raunin da suka samu a lokacin zanga-zangar, kamar yadda manema labarai na yankin suka ruwaito.
Rashin kwanciyar hankali a yankin da ke neman 'yancin kai bai ragu ba har shekara guda bayan kuri'ar raba gardama da Madrid ta ayyana ba bisa ka'ida ba a ranar 1 ga Oktoba, wanda 'yan Catalonia masu neman raba gardama ke murna da shi.
Yawanci masu jefa kuri'a sun zabi 'yancin kai duk da cewa halarta ba ta da yawa saboda wadanda suka yi adawa da rabuwa sun yi boycott a zaben.
Hukumomin Catalonia sun ce kusan mutane 1,000 ne suka ji rauni a cikin rikice-rikicen da suka faru a bara bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi kokarin dakatar da gudanar da zabe a wuraren zabe a fadin yankin.
Kungiyoyin masu neman 'yancin kai sun kwashe daren Juma'a a kan titi don hana zanga-zangar nuna goyon baya ga 'yan sandan kasar.
An gudanar da zanga-zanga, amma masu zanga-zangar sun tilasta su bi wata hanya.
Narcis Termes, mai shekara 68, wani mai aikin lantarki da ya halarci zanga-zangar 'yan tawaye tare da matarsa, ya ce ba ya fatan Catalonia ta sami 'yancin kai.
Mun yi ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da suka fi muhimmanci a rayuwarmu a shekarar da ta shige.
Na ga iyayena suna kuka don farin cikin samun damar kada kuri'a, amma yanzu mun makale, in ji shi.
Duk da samun gagarumar nasara a zaben yanki na watan Disamba da ya gabata, jam'iyyun 'yancin kai na Catalonia na fuskantar matsala a wannan shekara saboda fitattun shugabannin su na gudun hijira ko kuma a tsare suna jiran shari'a saboda rawar da suka taka wajen shirya kuri'ar raba gardama da kuma sanarwar 'yancin kai.
Joan Puig, wani mai aikin injiniya mai shekara 42, wanda ya yi amfani da wayar tarho wajen yin fim na zanga-zangar goyon bayan 'yan sanda, ya ce 'yan siyasa ne suka jawo wannan rikici.
"Yanayin yana daɗa tsanani", in ji shi.
