Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga fushin jam'iyyar Democrat
"Zaɓen da aka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh ya nuna cewa an ƙi amincewa da mugun da kuma abin kunya da jam'iyyar Democrat ke yi", in ji Trump a taron da aka yi a birnin Wheeling, na jihar West Virginia.
Trump ya ce Kavanaugh ya sha wahala daga fushin jam'iyyar Democrat a lokacin da ake neman zaben.
Kavanauh ya shaida wa majalisar dattawa a ranar Alhamis, kuma ya yi watsi da zargin da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi na cin zarafin shekaru da yawa da suka gabata lokacin da suke matasa.
