Ƙungiyar AMLO ta Mexico ta yi alkawarin ba za ta yi amfani da sojoji ba don yaƙi da 'yan ƙasar.
Dan takarar shugabancin Mexico Andres Manuel Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da karfin soja ba kan 'yan kasa yayin da kasar ke gab da cika shekaru 50 da kisan gillar da aka yi wa daliban.
Lopez Obrador a ranar Asabar a Tlatelolco Square ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da sojojinsa ba akan mutanen Mexico.
Sojoji sun harbe mutane 300 a lokacin da ake zanga-zanga a wannan filin a ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin ɗalibai na hagu suka soma yaɗuwa a Latin Amirka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin tallafa wa matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kowane wata ga waɗanda ke karatu da kuma buɗe ƙarin jami'o'in jama'a kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da kuma rashin ilimi ne ke janyo matasa zuwa 'yan ta'adda.
Amurka za ta ninka jarinta a fannin fasaha na wucin gadi
"Yayin da kasar Sin ke kara samun karfi a fannin kere kere, Amurka za ta ninka kudaden da take zuba jari a fannin bincike", in ji mai zuba jari a fannin kere kere Kai Fu Leeu, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan tsokaci ya biyo bayan da sassa daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka suka sanar da tsare-tsaren da suka shafi ilimin kere kere, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata dabara ta musamman game da ilimin kere kere.
A halin yanzu, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirin ta a bara, inda take da burin zama kasa ta farko da ta fara kirkirar AI a shekarar 2030.
"Haɗa kasafin kuɗi na bincike na fasaha zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, saboda duk sauran ƙasashe suna bin Amurka da nisa kuma muna neman babban abu na gaba a cikin ilimin kere kere", in ji Lee.
"Haɗaɗa zuba jari zai iya ninka damar samun babban ci gaba a fannin ilimin kere kere a Amurka", in ji Lee a cikin wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee wanda littafinsa mai suna "AI Great Powers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" aka buga a wannan watan ta hanyar kamfanin buga littattafai na Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, shi ne babban daraktan kamfanin Sinovation Ventures wanda ke zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a kasar Sin, Face++.
A shekarun 1980s, a Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya ci nasara a kan mafi kyawun wasan kwaikwayo na Amurka, Othello, kuma daga baya ya zama darektan bincike na Microsoft da shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya yaba wa gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata, kamar su Advanced Research Projects na Tsaro, da kuma Gasar Robotics ta Hukumar, kuma ya yi tambaya a kan lokacin da za a gudanar da na gaba don gano sabbin masu hangen nesa.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amirka sukan yi aiki tuƙuru don su sami tallafin gwamnati.
