Tauraruwar Game of Thrones Kit Harington ya yi watsi da cutar da ke cutar da maza
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar Jon Snow mai ɗaukar takobi a cikin mummunan tunanin HBO na Game of Thrones.
Amma ɗan wasan mai shekara 31 ya ƙi yarda da ra'ayin cewa jarumi ɗan iska ne, ya ce irin waɗannan ayyuka a talabijin sukan sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su yi ƙarfi don a daraja su.
A cikin wata hira da jaridar The Sunday Times Culture, Kit ya ce ya yi imanin cewa "wani abu ya ɓace" kuma ya yi mamakin yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa ta maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri wata abokiyar aikinsa mai suna Rose Leslie 'yar shekara 31 daga cikin jerin wasan kwaikwayon Game of Thrones, ya yarda cewa yana son ya "yi gaba da fuskantar" wannan matsalar.
"Ni kaina ina jin na yanke shawara a wannan lokacin" "inda muka yi kuskure da namiji?" ya tambaya.
"Me aka koya wa maza, yayin da suka girma, dangane da matsalar da muke fuskanta yanzu?"
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin, ta wurin halayen maza da yawa a kan fuska, na iya zama wani ɓangare na dalilin ƙaruwar mazaunin guba.
Ya ci gaba da cewa: "Me aka haifa, kuma me aka koya?
Me ake koya wa yara a talabijin da kuma a kan titi da zai sa su ji cewa dole ne su kasance da irin halayen maza?
Ina tsammanin wannan shine babbar tambaya a zamaninmu - ta yaya zamu canza wannan?
Domin akwai wani abu da ya faru da yaran.
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi fim ba game da wasan kwaikwayon na Game of Thrones bayan ya ƙare a lokacin bazara mai zuwa kuma ya ce ya "ƙare tare da fadace-fadace da dawakai".
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai yi fim a wani sabon wasan kwaikwayon wasan kwaikwayon True West na Sam Shepard, labarin wani mai samar da fim da ɗan'uwansa mai fashi.
A kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa ya ji cewa saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun abin da ya faru da shi yayin yin fim ɗin Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata a lokacin da nake yin wannan shirin, wanda ya ba ni iyali da kuma rayuwa mai zuwa", in ji shi.
Rose ta yi fim a cikin wani shirin almara na Emmy wanda ya lashe lambar yabo ta kyauta, wanda ya yi wasa da Ygritte, ƙaunar John Snow na Kit.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin cututtuka da kashi 14 cikin dari
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da dubu 820 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar.
An samu sabbin mutane kusan 40,000 a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka na kamuwa da cutar ana yada su ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda canji ne daga baya.
A dā, cutar HIV tana yaɗuwa sosai a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin ta wurin ƙarin jini da ke ɗauke da cutar.
A wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan, hukumar kiwon lafiya ta kasar Sin ta ce, ba a samun mutane da yawa da ke kamuwa da cutar ta HIV ta wannan hanyar.
Duk da haka, kowace shekara adadin mutanen da suke da HIV da AIDS yana ƙaruwa da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i na ci gaba da zama matsala tsakanin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma ana cewa ana nuna wa LGBT wariya sosai.
Bincike ya nuna cewa saboda ra'ayoyin da suka dace a kasar, kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin 100 na mazajen da suke yin jima'i da mazaje za su yi aure.
Yawancin cututtuka da ake samu a irin wannan dangantaka suna faruwa ne domin rashin kāriya a lokacin jima'i.
