Ana iya ganin baiwar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma wasan kwaikwayo yana da ban sha'awa sosai kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman ma yanzu da sunayen fina-finai masu tsanani kamar 007 da Mission Impossible da kansu suna ba da abubuwan wasan kwaikwayo.
