Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa, kusan mutane miliyan 649 a dukan duniya sun amfana daga tanadin da aka yi musu.
Wasu daga cikin muhimman alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta masu zuba jari da masu gudanar da ayyukan a Burtaniya da ke da niyyar taimakawa yara su samu ci gaba zuwa ga iyawarsu, tare da alkawarin cewa bayan karbar tweets sama da 4700 daga 'yan kasa da kasa, za su samar da dala miliyan 35 domin taimakawa Rwanda wajen kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a yankin.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatocin kasa da kuma 'yan kasa na duniya, kamar ku, za mu iya kawo rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin abin tunawa a tarihi", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition Foundation, a wani taron jama'a a London a watan Afrilu na shekarar 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki matakai sama da 5,000 da suka shafi inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da kudade ga wani shiri mai suna The Power of Nutrition wanda zai samar da tallafin abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara miliyan 5.
A amsa ga wata tambaya da aka fi yi a shafinta, wadda ta ce: "Me ya sa kuke ganin za mu iya kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci?"
