Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "ta'addanci" ta hanyar "tallan farfaganda".
Mako guda bayan jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu na talla a jaridar Amurka da ke tallata amfanin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da yin amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi tsokaci kan wani labarin da aka bayar a jaridar China Daily a babban jaridar Iowa, Des Moines Register, bayan ya zargi China da son tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, abin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin shiga cikin zaben Amurka ya nuna wani sabon mataki na kara matsin lamba kan kasar Sin da jami'an Amurka suka bayyana wa kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
Ko da yake yana da kyau gwamnatocin ƙasashen waje su yi talla don inganta cinikayya, Beijing da Washington suna cikin yakin cinikayya da ke ƙaruwa wanda ya haifar da hauhawar haraji kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su.
An yi amfani da fansa da China ta yi a farkon yakin cinikayya don cin zarafin masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
A wata kasida a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya ce China "yanzu tana ninka wannan cin zarafin ta hanyar tura tallace-tallace na farfaganda a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"Ta hanyar yada farfagandarsu, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da 'yancin jarida ta hanyar sanya talla a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A akasin wannan, a kan kantin sayar da jaridu a titunan Beijing, za ku ga ƙarancin muryoyin adawa kuma ba za ku ga wani ainihin tunani na ra'ayoyi daban-daban da mutanen Sin za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin China ba saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin matsin lamba na Jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa wasu manyan jaridun kasar Sin sun ki amincewa da buga labarin sa, duk da cewa bai bayyana ko wane ne ba.
Masu sharhi sun ce, Kavanaugh ya yi watsi da 'yan Republican da suka yi zabe a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara.
Da yake yawancin 'yan Republican suna goyon bayan wanda zai tsaya takarar kotun koli Bret Kavanaugh kuma suna kare shi kan zargin cin zarafin mata da dama, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa hakan zai haifar da mummunan martani a lokacin zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, musamman tsakanin mata.
An yi tashin hankali sosai a taron, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'unsu.
Ba za a iya dawo da irin wannan abu ba, in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka wallafa a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya nuna shakkar cewa, na karshe da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi na neman a gudanar da bincike na FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba, ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar masu ci gaba ta MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jaridar Washington, D.C. ta ruwaito.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a masu zanga-zanga sun rera waka "Hotuna sun zo!" suna zanga-zanga a cikin zauren majalisar dattawa yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka shirya ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Himma da himmar 'yan Democrat za su wuce duk wani zato", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani mai sharhi kan siyasa.
Mutane suna cewa sun riga sun kai matakin da ya kamata, kuma hakan gaskiya ne.
Amma kuma za su iya zama masu tsayi, musamman a tsakanin mata a cikin unguwannin karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda, ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, sau da yawa ba sa zuwa zaɓen.
Ko da kafin Ford ta yi shaida a fili inda ta bayyana dalla-dalla zargin da ta yi na cin zarafin da dan takarar babban alkalin kotun ya yi, manazarta sun yi hasashen cewa za a iya samun mummunar amsa idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da hakan.
"Wannan rikici ne ga tsohuwar jam'iyyar", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National Committee, a farkon makon da ya gabata, NBC News ta ruwaito.
"Ba wai kawai batun jefa kuri'a a kwamitin ba ne ko kuma kuri'ar karshe ko an tura Kavanaugh a kan kujera, amma kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka dauki wannan lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, daraktan kungiyar Priorities USA, kungiyar da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat.
Amma, jama'ar Amirka sun nuna cewa sun rabu biyu game da wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, kuma sun fi karkata zuwa gare shi.
Wani sabon bincike da YouGov ya fitar ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da gaskiyar shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun tabbata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan matsin lamba da Flake ya yi, FBI tana binciken zargin da Ford ya yi, tare da akalla mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez, in ji jaridar The Guardian.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata hari a lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta ce wani ɗan takarar babban kotu ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a wani biki a lokacin da take karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet domin ya dauki Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa sabuwar kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke ci gaba bisa tsarin Berners-Lee na Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda za a adana bayanan su da kuma mutanen da za a ba su damar samun damar wasu bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi waƙar cewa manufar da ke bayan Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi yana tunanin farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar keɓaɓɓen ajiyar bayanan yanar gizo ko POD.
Za ka iya samun jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalanda, laburaren waƙa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na kanka da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna kan burauzar a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da adana bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne, yanke shawara game da wanda zai iya samun damar abin da ke cikin bayanan gaba ɗaya na masu amfani ne.
Kamfanin ya kira wannan "karfafawa ta sirri ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce, kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, da hanyoyin aiki, da kuma ƙwarewar da ta dace don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu ya kunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu injiniyoyi da suka sanya hannu kan yarjejeniyar aiki a kan wannan aikin, da kuma wata kungiya ta masu shirye-shirye masu sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu ci gaba daga ko'ina cikin duniya sun sami damar gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su yi sauyi na gaba daya wanda zai sauya dukkan tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
Ba ma neman izininsu.
A cikin wani sakon da ya wallafa a shafinsa na Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa, "Mishin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi da kuma samar da mahalli na kasuwanci domin kare mutuncin da kuma ingancin sabuwar hanyar sadarwa da aka gina a Solida".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya sauya Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Ko da yake ya fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance wanda ya kafa kuma shugaban World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo ta Duniya da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da zamanin yanar gizo na gaba", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: Bikin da aka ba wa firist da ya yi yaƙi a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya lambar yabo ta Victoria
An yi bikin girmama firist na Anglican wanda aka ba shi lambar Victoria Cross a matsayin mai yaƙi a yakin duniya na farko a garinsa shekaru 100 bayan haka.
Lt. Col. Bernard Vann ya lashe kyautar ne a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba, 1918 a wani hari da aka kai a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi, kuma bai taɓa sanin cewa ya sami babban gata na yaƙi na Britaniya ba.
'Ya'yansa biyu sun gano wani abin tunawa a wani biki da aka yi a birnin Rushden da ke Northamptonshire a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, Michael Vann, ya ce yana da "alamar ban mamaki" cewa za a gano dutsen daidai shekaru 100 bayan aikin da kakansa ya yi wanda ya ba shi wannan girmamawa.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya ja-goranci rundunarsa a kan Canal St. Quentin, a cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai ƙarfi daga filin yaƙi da kuma injin injiniya.
Daga baya ya shiga cikin sahun gaba kuma tare da "ƙarfin gwiwa" ya jagoranci ƙungiyar gaba kafin ya yi ta gudu zuwa kan bindiga kuma ya kashe mutane uku daga cikin rukunin soja.
Wani dan Jamus ne ya kashe Laftanar Janar Vann a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba, 1918, wato fiye da wata guda kafin a kawo karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan da kakansa ya yi "abu ne da na sani ba zan taɓa iya cim ma ba, kuma hakan yana motsa ni in kasance mai tawali'u".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa Dr. James Vann sun kuma kafa kambi bayan bikin, wanda ƙungiyar mawaƙa ta Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ta gudanar.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin daɗin shiga cikin bikin kuma ya kara da cewa, "Yadda jarumi na gaskiya yake nunawa ta hanyar goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su bayar".
Masu son wasan Mixed Martial Arts sun kwana suna kallon Bellator 206 amma an ba su Peppou
Ka yi tunanin wannan: kana zama a farke dukan dare kana kallon jerin wasannin Bellator 206 har sai ka kasa ganin babban taron.
A San Jose, an yi wasannin guda 13 ciki har da shida a jerin sunayen, kuma a Burtaniya, an nuna su a daren kan Channel 5.
Da karfe shida na safe, daidai lokacin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald suka shirya don karawa, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamaki lokacin da aka katse watsa shirye-shiryen Peppa Pig.
Mutane da yawa ba su ji daɗi ba domin sun yi barci da sassafe domin suna fama.
Wani mai son fim ya bayyana katsewar shirin na yara a Twitter a matsayin "wani irin mugun wasa".
"Dangane da dokokin jihar, wannan abun ba shi da kyau a watsa shi a karfe shida na safe, don haka sai suka sauya zuwa shirin yara", in ji Dave Schwartz, babban mataimakin shugaban kasuwanci da sadarwa na Bellator, lokacin da aka tambaye shi game da watsa shirye-shiryen.
"Yup, 'Purple Peppa' ne wannan.
Shugaban Bellator, Scott Coker, ya ce zai daidaita jadawalin sa don ya hada da masu kallo daga Burtaniya a nan gaba.
"Lokacin da na yi la'akari da sake fasalin, ina tsammanin za mu iya yin wani abu", in ji Coker.
Amma, ana watsa shirye-shiryen a 6 na safe a ranar Lahadi, kuma ba za mu iya yin kome ba har sai ranar Lahadi ta zo, sa'ad da ranar Litinin ta zo.
Amma muna kan aiki.
Ku yi imani da ni, lokacin da aka katse watsa shirye-shiryen, akwai wasiƙu da yawa da ba su da abokantaka.
Mun yi ƙoƙarin gyara shi, muna tunanin cewa matsala ce ta fasaha.
Amma ba haka ba ne. Matsalar ƙasa ce.
Ina iya yi muku alkawari cewa ba za a sake yin hakan ba.
Za mu ci gaba da yin gwagwarmaya biyar maimakon shida, kamar yadda muke yi a yau.
Wannan ba labari ba ne.
Tom Daley ya ji cewa yana da kasa a batun jima'i
Dan wasan tsere na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin kasa da wasu saboda jima'i - amma hakan ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa don ya yi nasara.
Wani mutum mai shekara 24 ya ce har ya kai makarantar sakandare bai san cewa "kowa kamar ni yake ba".
A cikin wata sanarwa da ya bayar ga Radio 4 Desert Island Disks, wanda Lauren Laverne ke gudanarwa, ya ce yana magana ne game da 'yancin 'yan luwadi domin ya ba wa wasu "bege".
Ya kuma ce cin gasar Olympics ba shi da muhimmanci tun da ya zama uba.
Mai gabatar da shirin Kirsty Young ta dauki hutun watanni saboda rashin lafiya.
Da ya bayyana a matsayin mai son karuwanci a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce lokacin da yake girma, yana jin "kasa da sauran mutane" saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba don son yara maza da mata".
Ya ce, "Har zuwa yau, wannan jin kasa da bambanci da sauran mutane sune ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni iko da ƙarfi don in yi nasara".
Ya ce yana son ya tabbatar mata cewa shi wani ne, don kada ya sa kowa ya yi sanyin gwiwa idan suka gano cewa shi ma mutum ne.
Gwarzon dan wasan Olympics sau biyu ya zama babban mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da fitowarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Australia don yin kira ga kasashe da dama da su yanke hukuncin yin luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi magana a fili domin yana farin ciki da ya iya rayuwa a fili ba tare da sakamako ba kuma domin yana son ya ba da bege ga wasu.
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce abin mamaki ne ya fada cikin soyayya da wani mutum - dan fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013.
Daley ya auri wani ɗan Oscar da ya girme shi da shekara 20 a shekarar da ta shige, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taɓa zama masa matsala ba.
"Lokacin da kake matashi kana fuskantar abubuwa da yawa" - ya tuna lokacin da ya fara gasar Olympics lokacin yana da shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya wanda ya fuskanci irin wannan tashin hankali da rashin daidaito.
A watan Yuni, sun zama iyayen wani ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce wannan ya canja ra'ayinsa.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk maganar da za a yi shi ne game da samun lambar zinare", in ji shi.
"Ka san abin da, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
Robbie ne lambar zinare ta gasar Olympics.
Sunan ɗansa Robert ne, wanda mahaifinsa ya yi wa suna Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana ɗan shekara 40 bayan an gano cewa yana da ciwon ƙwaƙwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambaya shi ne ko sun samu tikitin zuwa London 2012 - domin yana son ya kasance a gaba.
"Ban iya gaya masa ba, 'Baba, ba za ka daɗe a nan ba ka zama na farko,'" in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa sa'ad da yake numfashi, kuma sai da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu, sai na fahimci cewa ba shi da iko", in ji shi.
Daley ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shine abin da na yi mafarki na tsawon rayuwata - don tsalle a gaban masu sauraro a wasannin Olympics, ba a taɓa jin daɗi ba", in ji shi.
Wannan kuma shine abin da ya ba da shawarar zaɓi na farko na "Proud" na Heather Small wanda ya yi ta'aziyya a cikinsa yayin shirye-shiryen wasannin Olympics kuma wanda yake fushi da shi koyaushe.
Ana watsa shirye-shiryen Desert Island Discs a tashar BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na BST.
Mickelson ya fita daga kan benci a gasar cin kofin Ryder a ranar Asabar
