Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya na neman hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara a birnin New York na neman a yanke wa Sayful Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin New York - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba tun shekarar 1953.
An ce Saipov, mai shekaru 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a gefen yammacin Manhattan, inda ya kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma masu hawan keke da suka tsinci kansu a hanyarsa a watan Oktoba
Don a ba da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya yi niyyar kashe mutane takwas da kuma yi musu mummunan rauni, a cewar sanarwar da aka gabatar na neman hukuncin kisa, da aka shigar a yankin kudancin New York.
Dukkanin waɗannan abubuwa biyu suna haifar da hukuncin kisa, bisa ga takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta yanke masa hukunci a kan laifin da ya kunshi abubuwa 22, wanda ya hada da laifukan kisa guda takwas da kuma cin hanci da rashawa, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sukan yi amfani da su wajen shari'ar aikata laifuka, da kuma laifukan tashin hankali da kuma lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma tunani sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna bayyana yadda Saipov ya kai harin a matsayin "m, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa iyalan da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernán Ferrucci, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandra Damián Pagnuccas rauni, lahani da kuma asarar rai", in ji sanarwar da aka bayar.
Mutane biyar da suka mutu 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
Shekara goma ke nan da aka daina yin shari'ar kisa a Kudancin New York.
An zargi wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da kisan wasu dillalai biyu na miyagun kwayoyi, amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumba na shekarar 2009.
An yi hukuncin kisa a ƙarshe a cikin shari'ar tarayya a New York, a 1953, lokacin da aka kashe ma'aurata Julius da Ethel Rosenberg bayan an yanke musu hukuncin laifin yin leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe Rosenbergs a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953, a kan kujerar lantarki.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, Saipov, ɗan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin tuba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗi game da abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa ya sa ya kai harin, kamar yadda takardar tuhumar ta ce.
Ya kuma nemi a rataye tutar ISIS a cikin dakin asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan abubuwa 22 da ake tuhumarsa da su.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin lauyoyin gwamnati na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce sun yi takaici sosai da shawarar da kotun ta yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon amincewa da hukuncin daurin rai da rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar sakewa ba, zai kara tsawaita ciwon da abubuwan da suka faru suka yi wa duk wanda ke ciki", in ji Patton.
A baya, tawagar lauyoyin Saipov ta nemi a dakatar da karar.
