Yadda Yakin Ciniki Tsakanin Amurka Da China Zai Iya Zama Mai Kyau Ga Beijing
An yi ta magana a kan farawar yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma yayin da yakin bai gama ba, rarrabuwar kawuna tsakanin kasashen na iya amfanar Beijing a dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Donald Trump, shugaban Amurka, ya ba da gargadi na farko a farkon wannan shekarar, yana haraji kan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da aluminum.
Mafi girman tashin hankali a wannan makon ya zo ne da sabbin haraji da suka shafi kayayyakin da suka kai dala biliyan 200, a zahiri sun sanya haraji kan rabin kayayyakin da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
A duk lokacin da aka yi wannan, Beijing ta yi ta mayar da martani, kuma kwanan nan ta kafa haraji na kashi biyar zuwa goma a kan kayayyakin da suka kai dala biliyan 60.
China ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta mayar wa Amurka da hari, kuma babu shakka tattalin arzikin duniya na biyu ba zai daina ba.
Za a iya samun komawar Washington ta hanyar sassauci, amma yin biyayya ga Amurka a fili zai zama abin ƙyama ga Xi Jinping, shugaban kasar Sin.
Amma masana sun ce idan Beijing ta yi wasa da kyau, matsin lamba na yakin cinikayya na Amurka na iya ba da goyon baya ga China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin kasashen biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa saurin yanke shawara a siyasa a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da rushewar tattalin arziki a kasashen biyu ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu sa ido suka yi imani", in ji Abigail Grace, wata jami'ar kimiyya mai kula da tunani mai mahimmanci da ke mayar da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta Amurka.
Syria ta "shirya" don dawo da 'yan gudun hijira, in ji ministan harkokin wajen kasar
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta mayar da 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai, kuma ta yi kira ga gwamnati da ta taimaka wajen sake gina kasar da ta yi fama da rikici na tsawon shekaru bakwai.
A jawabinsa ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Wajen Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayin kasar na inganta.
"Yau, yanayin da ke kan hanya ya fi kwanciyar hankali da tsaro saboda ci gaban da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da aikin gyara wuraren da ta'addanci ya lalata domin dawo da al'amuran al'umma cikin yanayi na al'ada.
Yanzu duk sharuɗɗan da suka dace don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai zuwa ƙasar da suka bari saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na kai tsaye da aka mayar da hankali kan rayuwarsu ta yau da kullun da rayuwa sun cika.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa fiye da 'yan Syria miliyan 5.5 ne suka gudu daga kasar tun lokacin da aka fara yakin a shekarar 2011.
Mutane miliyan shida da suke zaune a kasar suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria na bukatar taimako wajen sake gina kasar da aka lalata.
Amma ya ce ba zai amince da taimakon da aka ba shi ba, kuma ba zai amince da taimakon da ƙasashen da suka tallafa wa tawayen suka bayar ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Team Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018, inda ta doke tawagar Amurka da ci 16.5 ̶ 10.5 a filin Le Golf National da ke kusa da Paris, Faransa.
A yanzu haka, Amurka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kambin yayin da tawagar Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a kusan dukkanin gasar, a kan rami na 16 a par 3, ya jefa kwallon cikin ruwa a bugun farko, ya bar Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a duk zagaye kuma ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa hudu da suka taba kaiwa 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara wannan tsari a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya yi watsi da Thorbjorn Olesen dan Denmark, dan wasan da ya fi kowacce tawagar Turai a matsayi na biyar da hudu.
Dustin Johnson, dan wasan da ya fi kowa a duniya, ya ci 2 da 1 a hannun dan Ingila Ian Poulter wanda wataƙila shi ne dan wasansa na ƙarshe a gasar Ryder.
